{
  "stem": "268.6",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And a repertoire of Polish songs came in handy again in that camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They took the harmonica away from me because the commandant gave me, actually, two harmonicas then.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then I-- from each camp, they transfer you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You, you, you get a new, striped uniform, a number, and a new-- a different wardrobe, different, different prison garbs.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they took everything away, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They stripped you naked.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I lost that harmonica.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I started singing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I was assigned to this one barrack.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was a Polish-- again, I had a miraculous thing happen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "A Polish Blockalteste-- a Blockalteste was the second one in command to the Lageralteste, to, to the commandant, who was the second one in command to the German SS commandant.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He was in charge of, perhaps, maybe 150 or maybe 200.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It depends how many people are in one barrack.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But he was-- he was a murderer, this guy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I can still see him-- short guy, maybe 5' 3', 5' 4', kind of bow-legged, blond.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] He had a reddish face, not-- complexion not too clear, like, like-- they call it-- they call it [GERMAN], like pox, pox-- like smallpox.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And that's the kind of face he had.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And mean-looking and very mean-- he would-- he would derive pleasure of beating up on a person or killing him and split somebody's head open.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "This is how they would treat us in Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "You don't know nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "This is what they used to do in Mauthausen when I would-- he would take it out-- because he, he was already in camp, like, three years.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So he would take it out on us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Yeah, you Jews and all that, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But he took a liking to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
